### Sample endpoint (for connection testing)

GET http://localhost:5066/weatherforecast

### List nodes

GET http://localhost:5066/nodes

### Get node

GET http://localhost:5066/nodes/testnode

### Create or update node

POST http://localhost:5066/nodes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "testnode",
  "vmSize": "Standard_D2as_v5"
}

### Stop node

POST http://localhost:5066/nodes/testnode/stop

### Start node

POST http://localhost:5066/nodes/testnode/start

### Remove node

DELETE http://localhost:5066/nodes/testnode
